Body:
Description: Hi Team,

We are facing the issue while upload the image & video mp4 files in AWS S3 BUCKET and all that is not working and we have already add in allow list. all the whitelist domain could you please check and resolve the issue asap.
Invitation updated. Attendees: Andre Le Roux
Invitation updated. Attendees: No attendees listed
Invitation updated. Attendees: Andre Le Roux, SANJAY KASHYAP

What We've Learned Updated: The users uploads of files were blocked to the AWS S3 domain due to a CAP policy which is configured to block the transfers of file types.  The issue was that the AWS S3 domain was not added correctly to the DPI URL / domain allowed list.  After we added the correct format of domain the issue was solved.
Next Steps Updated: The issue was resolved on call, case can be closed.
